  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Rail holidays in Europe</h2>
<p><span>Looking for a new way to see Europe? Put your holiday on the right track and step aboard a rail holiday to Europe. This is your ticket to the great outdoors, where you'll be treated to some of the most stunning views Europe has to offer. </span></p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095152/bernina_express_sommer.jpg?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="rail holidays europe" data-udi="umb://media/01a6e311c948429885f1b808c3255fb1" /></p>
<p>Departing from St Pancras, London, we offer unforgettable rail journeys to some of the most breath-taking destinations in <a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a>, as well as selected resorts in <a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a>. So if you're looking for a new kind of walking adventure that's off the beaten track, but still within reach of all the top sights and sounds then take a look at our rail holidays.</p>
<p> </p>
<h2>Our Rail holidays</h2>
<p>We've got your ticket to the most relaxing, luxurious travel experience in Europe. <span>Our rail holidays offer an exceptional European travel experience, all from the comfort of your train seat. Whether you crave the elegance of the <a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line">Goldenpass Line</a> or the breath-taking views of the Swiss Alps on the <a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express">Glacier Express</a>, we have you covered.</span></p>
<p><span><strong>Call to book: <a href="tel:01483 791 111" class="InfinityNumber">01483 791 111</a></strong></span></p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Iconic rail journeys</h3>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express"><strong>The Glacier Express</strong></a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095157/rail-holiday-1.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="rail holidays europe" data-udi="umb://media/2c21ccf1890c494baf6f5e115f9f5c6b" /></p>
<p><strong>Switzerland: </strong><strong>Interlaken<span> </span>– Zermatt – Davos/Klosters</strong></p>
<p><strong>10 or 11 nights</strong></p>
<p>If you love mountains, this is your train trip. Our 10 or 11 night independent rail holiday provides you with unforgettable views between <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a> and either <a data-udi="umb://document/527f062dda374fee961e7ca5209c3d26" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/graubunden-region/davos" title="Davos">Davos</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/5cdc3bd60ed74827b457178da3c4090e" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/graubunden-region/klosters" title="Klosters">Klosters</a>. The specially designed panoramic carriages unlock superb views over the Swiss Alps.</p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express" class="c-btn">Find out more</a><a data-udi="umb://document/a9a7db62204445c9afab9589b4941af8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a9a7db62204445c9afab9589b4941af8}" title="Slovenia Savings"></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line"><strong>GoldenPass Line</strong></a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095158/swiss-rail-goldenpass.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="GoldenPass Line Rail Holiday" data-udi="umb://media/0e2ec2eb61e14d7289b5bac85cbe8b1f" /></p>
<p><strong>Switzerland: </strong><strong>Montreux – Wengen – Lake Lucerne</strong></p>
<p><strong>10 or 11 nights</strong></p>
<p>Visit three regions of<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a><span> </span>on this three centre rail holiday which includes a trip on the<span> </span><a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-switzerland/goldenpass-line" title="GoldenPass Line">GoldenPass line</a>. On your holiday you’ll have the opportunity to explore the Lavaux Vineyards, the mountainous Jungfrau area and the historical sites of <a data-udi="umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/56819e7662924ccf91baa56999b5cbef}" title="Lucerne">Lucerne</a>. </p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d8a3be3fd1dd4a9393a346df4f3e910c}" title="GoldenPass Line" class="c-btn">Find out more</a></div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Multi-centre rail holidays</h3>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3}" title="Venice, Florence &amp; Rome">Venice, Florence &amp; Rome</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095206/italy-by-rail.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="italy rail holidays" data-udi="umb://media/41597763d1ea40d7b1d991e9a402ab2d" /></p>
<p>Get a taste of Italy on this three-city tour from Venice to Rome. Visit galleries in Florence, wander along the Grand Canal in Venice and take in culture and history as you stroll through Rome's city centre. Take in the sights, sip on a rich espresso, and savour the finest wines on this unforgettable journey through the heart of Italy.<span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d878f477114346f99e5f102f64f0e4e3}" title="Venice, Florence &amp; Rome" class="c-btn">Find out more</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f}" title="Swiss Classic Tour">Swiss Classic Tour</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095156/swiss-rail-holiday.jpg?width=500&amp;height=270" alt="swiss classic tour" data-udi="umb://media/1b698dc01da042f0a44ff05ed99e67cd" /></p>
<p>This 10-day multi-centre holiday will take you on a journey of a lifetime through Switzerland's breath-taking landscapes, giving you a true taste of this stunning country. Brace yourself for an unforgettable adventure aboard two of the most spectacular panoramic journeys in the world: the <span><span class="ui-provider fz b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z ab ac ae af ag ah ai aj ak">Bernina</span></span> and <a data-udi="umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae29f8328e454cb08ae9ecf28f7078f4}" title="Glacier Express">Glacier Express</a>.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58868750b42d43d78a89df92df2b164f}" title="Swiss Classic Tour" class="c-btn">Find out more</a></div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
