<h2>Destinations you can reach by train from the UK</h2>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy">Italy</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095203/italy-holidays.jpg?width=317&amp;height=171" alt="Italy by rail" data-udi="umb://media/82b0db05ab4f471189e4cbbf8447612e" /></p>
<p>London to Italy by train is easy with Eurostar to Paris and Voyages SNCF to Italy. Daytime services include trips to <a data-udi="umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2575554a5b50446eb00d5bf533f317cd}" title="Milan">Milan</a> or high-speed trains through the Swiss Alps to <a data-udi="umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d421e04a79044babf8cafda30e31d4a}" title="Lake Como">Lake Como</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48" href="/{localLink:umb://document/476c8caf3fe84faab565f2d0f2e99f48}" title="Lake Maggiore">Lake Maggiore</a>. </p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a1a80922d88a43f8ba80b182c72e8904}" title="Italy" class="c-btn">View Italy holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland">Switzerland</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095200/switzerland.jpg?width=317&amp;height=171" alt="switzerland by rail" data-udi="umb://media/8c96ad88d99c40b2a16cbc2432d840fc" /></p>
<p>Take a scenic and comfortable journey to Switzerland by Eurostar from London to Paris, followed by a high-speed train to Geneva or Zurich with frequent direct connections to resorts.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/92803bd348ec48c1b64d53e77931172d}" title="Switzerland" class="c-btn">View Switzerland holidays</a></div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3><a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France">France</a></h3>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095198/france-by-rail.jpg?width=317&amp;height=171" alt="France by rail" data-udi="umb://media/44766c70827144f0b37374572fc28f19" /></p>
<p>Travel in style and arrive comfortably at your destination with high speed rail service from Paris to <a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/59d85c3607bf4fc5a291361000fe9db0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/59d85c3607bf4fc5a291361000fe9db0}" title="Lake Annecy">Annecy</a> and beyond. The fastest trains from Paris to Chamonix take around 5 hours and 30 minutes.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf" href="/{localLink:umb://document/20c1ee89e76c4eab9b98c48479361bdf}" title="France" class="c-btn">View France holidays</a></div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><strong>Step into summer with Inghams</strong></h2>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13089493/our-holidays-838x220.jpg?width=500&amp;height=131.2649164677804" alt="rail holidays europe" data-udi="umb://media/b40cf9d23b4a4012aaed9b15dfdb0eab" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ With over 85 years of experience you can trust us to deliver your perfect holiday.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ You'll have the reassurance and expert guidance of our reps when in resort.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️ Enjoy two guided walks per week in selected resorts*.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">✔️Flights from your choice of 15 regional airports, transfers and accommodation are included in your holiday.</p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Travel With Confidence</h2>
<p>When you book with us you can travel with confidence. <a data-udi="umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fa72be9e45bc442089252c6a18a0d2ae}" title="In Safe Hands">We’ve put extra measures in place </a>for your peace of mind. We’ll help keep both you and your money safe.</p>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13095389/inghams-in-safe-hands-charcoal.png?width=500&amp;height=126.45687645687646" alt="in safe hands" data-udi="umb://media/afba17a916e84fcc848acce5dda4f9c4" /></p>
<p><strong>Terms and Conditions</strong></p>
<p>**<span>Up to two guided walks per week are included in the following resorts: </span><a data-udi="umb://document/594483304a5f4b47844b444df2c9d975" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/austrian-tyrol/mayrhofen" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a><span>, <a data-udi="umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a71713291d5d4220aea1b806f34cd053}" title="Seefeld">Seefeld</a>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/ab49d5977a794ec7952da3e3d5adf48b" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/austria/saalbach-hinterglemm" title="Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm">Saalbach &amp; Hinterglemm</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/chamonix" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/a95b5199e8e04283bf8eeeabb42715fc" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/france/morzine" title="Morzine">Morzine</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/604dbba59ac64320ab6e9f1e89231a4c" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/lake-garda/limone" title="Limone">Limone</a><span>, <a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano">Merano</a>,<a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva"> Selva</a>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/9b6cf6eac79541f5850e141e41a071ab" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/slovenia/kranjska-gora" title="Kranjska Gora">Kranjska Gora</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/grindelwald" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a><span>, </span><a data-udi="umb://document/dd4c4793225641fcb24c0918a33714b3" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/bernese-oberland/wengen" title="Wengen">Wengen</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/switzerland/zermatt" title="Zermatt">Zermatt, </a><a data-udi="umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cad35d37f73d435087041e35025d1da8}" title="Funchal">Funchal</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f6d745a0efdf44b5b28bcd4bee55dbb1}" title="Canico">Caniço</a><span>. </span><span>All walks are subject to availability of local guides, weather conditions and maximum numbers. Where we cannot confirm your preferred option in resort, we will endeavour to offer an alternative subject to the above conditions. </span></p>
<p> </p>]]></bodyText>
